trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa `Dispose` när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden lämnar kvar det <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>oanvändbar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Efter att `Dispose`, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>var upptar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Släpper de ohanterade resurser som används av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.CatalogExportProvider"> </xref> och släpper du de hantera resurserna.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Frisläpp både hanterade och ohanterade resurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> att släppa endast resurser som inte hanteras.

trans-unit.source: Returns all exports that match the conditions of the specified import.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar alla exporter som matchar villkoren i den angivna importfilen.

trans-unit.source: Implementers should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and should not throw exceptions for cardinality-related mismatches.
trans-unit.target: Implementerare behandla inte kardinalitet-relaterade avvikelser som fel och utlösa inte undantag för kardinalitet-relaterade avvikelser.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the GetExportsCore method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> objects.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel om importen kräver exakt en export och providern har ingen matchande export eller fler än en, GetExportsCore-metoden ska returnera en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>samling <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>objekt.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>

trans-unit.source: The conditions of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"></xref> objects to be returned.
trans-unit.target: Villkoren i den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export"> </xref> objekt som ska returneras.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains all the exports that match the specified condition.
trans-unit.target: En samling som innehåller alla exporterna som matchar de angivna villkoren.
